            <li class="top-ten-list-item rmec nine">
                <div class="icon"><p class="go"><a href="" title="">GO</a></p></div>
                <p class="header">Replace or Modify the Electoral College</p>
                <p class="description">Move to a national popular vote or divide each stateâ€™s electors on a proportional basis
</p>
